{"tid":2497884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那2歲女遭同學掐頸咬面見血 Playgroup被斥扮和事佬卸責 網民：患了瘋狗症","createTime":"2021-04-20T22:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:55:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd2cbebca2f2c7d34bba400f18658c0bba3f720","tid":2497884,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T22:12:09.000Z","msg":"廣東深圳近日發生幼童咬人事件。一名2歲女童在早教機構（即playgroup）被年齡相若男童掐頸咬面見血，嚎哭2分鐘才被老師發現，女童臉部或會留疤破相。涉事機構事後只扮作「和事佬」，協助事主獲賠2萬元人民幣（下同，約2.4萬港元），被家長指摘逃避責任。網民批評涉事機構疏忽照顧，以及質疑男童家長的教育方法，甚至有人調侃男童患了瘋狗症才會亂咬人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210421/TYRFODZVX5BLVJCUD3Q2B5KYN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210421%2FTYRFODZVX5BLVJCUD3Q2B5KYN4%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f6fc70c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210421%2FTYRFODZVX5BLVJCUD3Q2B5KYN4%2F&h=25c1dda1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210421/TYRFODZVX5BLVJCUD3Q2B5KYN4/</a>"},{"pid":"07beb4c40a3c830e40a7bbbe5544f4295b980157","tid":2497884,"uid":364068,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"估啱国家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d85736b90f8de571e25eefdf76d373c0e8f732","tid":2497884,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"中國人本質"},{"pid":"d9d60dbe3b9044f952064e0f41d0bf33ad454d7d","tid":2497884,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"照咁睇，支那似乎爆發zombie 危機<br />\n<br />\n留係香港死路一條"},{"pid":"40edc72e1c9e11966bcce887794dede5a8fe7734","tid":2497884,"uid":115270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"同寵物展隻狗差唔多"},{"pid":"6c4f32c45a8ba2e76184416a5e34b5631768b399","tid":2497884,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c